Index: linux-2.6.23-rc8/arch/i386/kernel/ksysfs.c
===================================================================
--- /dev/null	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ linux-2.6.23-rc8/arch/i386/kernel/ksysfs.c	2007-10-12 11:21:05.000000000 +0800
